          <span class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Quvii</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          See everything. Subscribe to nothing. Local-first home security
          cameras for people who'd rather own than rent their data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white mt-0">Shop</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-none p-0">
          <li><a href="/products/" class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline">All cameras</a></li>
          <li><a href="/collections/indoor/" class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline">Indoor</a></li>
          <li><a href="/collections/outdoor/" class="text-sm text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline">Outdoor</a></li>
